  "texts": [
    "Although green finance benefits both the environment and economic development, supporting SDG 8, there are long-term vision challenges, technological risks, market and demand, reputational and social risks, and alignment with global trends (Gupta M. et al., 2023).",
    "Promising aspects of green finance include opportunities to promote and invest in environmentally conscious projects, which are key to fostering sustainable development while addressing pressing ecological concerns.",
    "The topic of \"sustainable energy access through climate finance\" highlights the role of sustainable and green finance in achieving the SDGs, particularly climate action (SDG 13) and economic development (SDG 8).",
    "Effective governance and transparency in climate finance are vital for SDG 16.",
    "Mobilizing private finance in regions such as Sub-Saharan Africa, where energy access and climate mitigation are critical, aligns with SDGs 7 and 17."
  ],
